:"講就兇狠"},{"pid":"a784e0a9c4963c7666b37fdc668e13673b8dbd56","tid":2028373,"uid":56219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:38:07.000Z","msg":"因為你講一句就唔立國安法, 唔多信....準備今日公佈詳情好過"},{"pid":"619f58e55d7de93dddf3550d4ab39b357ae3cff4","tid":2028373,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:46:37.000Z","msg":"我地要同共產黨對賭香港對世界經濟嘅影響力<br />\n賭美國守香港嘅決心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本來佢地日日扮一國兩制<br />\n搞個假法治搵黑警濫捕<br />\n搵紅官亂判<br />\n班鬼佬都無乜位入香港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">而家支共直接插旗撕破埋假面具<br />\n今次係我地香港人最後生機<br />\n成件串埋港共 黑警 紅官 賣港狗（開始有狗話佢地只係奉命行事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奉命賣港殺人？）<br />\n<br />\n共產黨以一國一制搞亂香港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n到時外國想淨係制裁班共狗又好<br />\n成個香港制裁都好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地都無得輸<br />\n因為無野差得過跟住落嚟落入支那手<br />\n變新疆2.0"},{"pid":"91651a2d13129c3fb29470e2d9ccc1895ceb071f","tid":2028373,"uid":95477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1bb7f4cb3c845567aa470c95ae39cceb8a53d0f5","tid":2028373,"uid":61547,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"4c82944ae54f48346666fe17e4940f9eb39fc954","tid":2028373,"uid":125727,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T20:03:19.000Z","msg":"明明關係法 美國既利益仲大過香港同中國<br />\n美國品牌公司都係想借香港打入中國市場 已家直接跳去上海都得<br />\n政府玩對賭  <br />\n<strong>真係唔信美國會為某國民主而放棄自身利益</strong><br />\n<br />\n如果美國唔取消關係法  所有之前抗爭都係白費 <br />\n安份守己做蝗"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T20:11:31.000Z","msg":"或者有啲人唔知<br />\n美國同其他國家好少有貿易順差<br />\n而香港係美國最大貿易順差既經濟體<br />\n即係美國係賺緊香港錢<br />\n而中國係香港貿易順差最大既來源地<br />\n即係香港係賺緊大陸錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單講美國係賺緊香港錢<br />\n而香港係賺緊大陸錢<br />\n<br />\n我都唔係好信美國會放棄最大貿易順差經濟體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過美國係有能力唔理貿易順差果筆錢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:47:29.000Z","msg":"大佬 唔係香港賺大陸錢<br />\n而係大陸要靠喺香港投資<br />\n來將人民幣轉換成其他貨幣"},{"pid":"95c5e3891c77f661710f412e20f6a5744a8b21a9","tid":2028373,"uid":268076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:48:34.000Z","msg":"制裁講左成半年有多班官都有哂兩手準備啦<br />\n我想黎一個措手不及嘅反擊"},{"pid":"abfb7f31356e42f08289c2859896c365648eacf7","tid":2028373,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ddf178ceb65ea670c94b328a55f41836ac11b6e","tid":2028373,"uid":88982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T00:01:34.000Z","msg":"我死唔緊要呀 最緊要拉埋支那一齊上路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1daa469c9e6d795d189785c3080874422ede44","tid":2028373,"uid":295407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2a586383505250ad4765b6872d52649307012588","tid":2028373,"uid":249794,"like":95,"dislike":4,"score":91,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T18:55:46.000Z","msg":"提案有排先實行到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T00:02:43.000Z","msg":"啱，其實唔駛咁大期望，<br />\n美國反中愈嚟愈激烈係必然嘅事，但佢唔會係你今日講完聽日就制裁，<br />\n剩係個人權法都搞咗成年。<br />\n過程一定好長，但香港人捱落去美國嘅制裁一定會到"},{"pid":"834e70a3dca36b75c395f1b21839c8561e40a9e4","tid":2028373,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T00:03:18.000Z","msg":"ul"},{"pid":"a8feb6472595fdee5afd89baad20aba645ae9ac9","tid":2028373,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T00:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee8ee91e5814b5649e177a315f954d46be056cdf","tid":2028373,"uid":77666,"like